<plot>On the ice, Toronto Maple Leaf Carl Brewer was a fast skating, highly skilled defenseman who didn't hesitate to start a fight. His biggest battle would come off the ice, however, when the four time all star took on the NHL Players Association's Executive Director, Alan Eagleson, in a legal battle that would eventually lead to Eagleson's imprisonment and change the game forever</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?570882</url></doc>
